{"tid":2439380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Greta Thunberg 批評拜登在氣候危機方面做得不夠","createTime":"2021-03-09T08:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T08:47:46.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5469913063899a375aea3dd2307d8508db8393e1","tid":2439380,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，近日瑞典&ldquo;環保少女&rdquo;格雷塔&middot;桑伯格（Greta Thunberg）批評美國總統喬&middot;拜登&ldquo;無視氣候變化的科學&rdquo;，她稱拜登在&ldquo;把氣候危機當成危機來對待&rdquo;方面做得不夠，指責他在這個問題上&ldquo;與科學不完全一致&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n今年18歲的桑伯格是青少年環保問題活動人士，以抨擊世界各國領導人的環保政策而聞名。當地時間3月7日晚，桑伯格被問及如何看待拜登政府在氣候變化問題處理上的表現。<br />\n<br />\n在一開始，桑伯格表示，自己只是個青少年，所以無權做這種類似於打分的事情，&ldquo;我對此的看法並不重要&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n但她繼續說，拜登的政策遠遠不夠，&ldquo;你應該看看科學，看看他的政策是否符合巴黎協議，是否將溫度控制在1.5攝氏度甚至2攝氏度之下&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我只是希望你們把氣候危機當作一場危機來對待&rdquo;，她說，但拜登並沒有這樣處理此事，而只是把氣候危機作為一個政治話題來對待。<br />\n<br />\n當被問及&ldquo;建議總統為應對氣候變化做什麼事&rdquo;時，桑伯格並未回答這個問題本身，但她說，讓人們參與進來是當務之急，&ldquo;我們現在需要提高人們的意識，創造輿論，把危機當作危機來對待。如果人們不了解現在面臨的危機，他們就不會向當選的領導人施壓&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n桑伯格還說，對於那些抱怨缺乏支持而無法改變環境政策的領導人，需要為他們實現目標建立一個後盾，那就是首先把危機當作危機來對待，再期待選民的支持和壓力，期待人們為氣候採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/biden-climate-policies-greta-thunberg-1574478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fbiden-climate-policies-greta-thunberg-1574478&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=de031be1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsweek.com/biden-climate-policies-greta-thunberg-1574478</a><br />\n<br />\nGreta Thunberg Says Science Shows Joe Biden Not Doing Enough on Climate Change"},{"pid":"358632ce357b683581892ee6bb8253c31022e70c","tid":2439380,"uid":70487,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻閪鬥撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b1428a0ae1311263d4ef7b1b87c0c9da5c41a5","tid":2439380,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"未過數!&nbsp;HOW&nbsp;DARE&nbsp;YOU<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e7d26be0cababda1b33e7cda3fa71a9557cba","tid":2439380,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/wo/888159/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fwo%2F888159%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=83f28f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fwo%2F888159%2F&h=119d682e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/wo/888159/</a><br />\n<br />\n十七歲的通貝里在Twitter發文表示，她從未參與黨政，但這「即將到來的美國大選，重要性大過一切」。她寫道：「從氣候變化的角度來看，這遠遠不足，你們當中許多人當然支持另一名候選人。但，我的意思是，你知道的，團結起來吧，讓大家都把票投給拜登。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0dfc1de598a609176d107d6a805c22e9290658","tid":2439380,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"Joe Biden Says Greta Thunberg Not Young Enough"},{"pid":"f823280af2ef393aa1c1d842bf276184bd84c005","tid":2439380,"uid":303037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/43646e38f914946768086c8525ca146e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2F43646e38f914946768086c8525ca146e.gif&h=57c96099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31abec794feeb690720fc8156881c0888ad056bc","tid":2439380,"uid":109780,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nAjMSD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nAjMSD.gif&h=eef22046&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b890de4953e9bd6c9b4fcd9054302fecd43fbf7","tid":2439380,"uid":133806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f823280af2ef393aa1c1d842bf276184bd84c005","tid":2439380,"uid":303037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.clickme.net/gallery/43646e38f914946768086c8525ca146e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clickme.net%2Fgallery%2F43646e38f914946768086c8525ca146e.gif&h=57c96099&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/4e4740e1869490fd8972df264d7bf55e/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F4e4740e1869490fd8972df264d7bf55e%2Ftenor.gif&h=cc984b3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2961d5ebc4af42bab123fe8da6269167693271a9","tid":2439380,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0dfc1de598a609176d107d6a805c22e9290658","tid":2439380,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"Joe Biden Says Greta Thunberg Not Young Enough"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6383a489008d01f9e883e912c730b8284a4079e","tid":2439380,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"biden: who<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec1e3c295dc312674c9bc074d3ad7904d749fb3","tid":2439380,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yqWPcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c